<doc id="955132" wikidata="Q7273269" url="?curid=955132" title="R-Mall">
<text>R Mall is a mall situated in Mulund, a suburb of Mumbai, India was opened in 2003. Developed by Runwal Developers Pvt. Ltd., the mall with a frontage of was designed by Chapman Taylor &amp; Partners (UK). R Mall is a 4-storeyed air-conditioned mall covering an area of approximately on each floor. The site includes a 7 level car parking facility. It is the second oldest mall in Mumbai, and the oldest in Mumbai Suburban district.

